        "job_description": "About Us:\n\nLevelUp is a jobtech matchmaking platform connecting companies with right tech fits. Our hiring Partners are currently seeking talented individuals to join as data Analyst\n\nSalary Range: 3-6 LPA based on interview performance\n\nJob Description:\n\nAs a Data Analyst, you will be responsible for interpreting data, analyzing results, and providing insights to support informed business decisions. You will work closely with stakeholders across various departments to understand their data needs and develop solutions to address them.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n\n1. Collect, clean, and preprocess data from various sources using Excel and SQL to ensure data quality and integrity.\n\n2. Perform exploratory data analysis using Python to identify trends, patterns, and insights.\n\n3. Develop and maintain reports, dashboards, and visualizations using Tableau/Power BI to communicate key findings to stakeholders.\n\n4. Collaborate with cross-functional teams to define analytical requirements and deliver actionable insights.\n\n5. Utilize statistical techniques and machine learning algorithms in Python to extract meaningful information from data.\n\n6. Conduct ad-hoc analyses and present findings to support strategic decision-making.\n\n7. Stay updated with the latest tools and techniques in data analysis and apply them to improve processes and workflows.\n\nRequirements:\n\n1. Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Statistics, Mathematics, Economics, or a related field.\n\n2. Proficiency in Excel for data manipulation and analysis.\n\n3. Strong SQL skills for querying and manipulating data from relational databases.\n\n4. Experience with Python for data analysis, including data manipulation, visualization, and statistical analysis.\n\n5. Proficiency in Tableau or Power BI for creating reports, dashboards, and visualizations.\n\n6. Excellent communication and presentation skills with the ability to convey technical information to non-technical audiences.",
