        "job_description": "Company Description:\n\nUnitedHealth Group is a health care and well-being company focused on improving access, affordability, outcomes, and experiences in the health care system. With 340,000 colleagues, we have three distinct businesses - United Health Pro, Optum and UnitedHealthcare - working together to deliver better health through technology, data, and high-quality care. Our mission is to help people live healthier lives and build a modern, value-based system of compassionate and equitable care. Join us as we improve care for our consumers and their communities.\n\nRole Description:\n\nThis is a contract role for a Business Data Analyst (Remote).\n\nAs a Business Data Analyst, you will be responsible for performing data analysis, statistics, and data modeling to support business decisions.\n\nYou will communicate your findings to stakeholders and provide insights to optimize business performance.\n\nThis is a remote role.\n\nQualifications:\n\nAnalytical Skills, Data Analytics, and Statistics\n\nExcellent verbal and written Communication skills\n\nData Modeling\n\nExperience in using data visualization tools\n\nProficiency in SQL and data querying\n\nProblem-solving and critical thinking abilities\n\nAttention to detail and accuracy\n\nExperience in the healthcare industry is a plus\n\nBachelor's degree in a relevant field, such as Statistics, Mathematics, or Business Analytics",
