        "job_description": "BRIEF\n\nCodingChiefs, a prominent name in technical staffing, is seeking an experienced Frontend Developer to contribute to the development of innovative websites and webshops for diverse clients.\n\nYour primary responsibility will be to leverage your expertise in WordPress, Lightspeed, and Shopify to assist in cutting-edge digital solutions.\n\nCLIENT DETAILS\n\nOur client helps businesses thrive online through creative web design, marketing strategies, and content creation. Their passionate team enjoys working with diverse clients and aims to develop projects that leave a lasting positive impact.\n\nThey stay ahead of the curve by actively researching industry trends and sharing their knowledge through dedicated websites.\n\nRESPONSIBILITIESAssist in developing Lightspeed / Shopify features / plugins for client projects\n\nHandle tickets and development of functionalities for client websites and webshops\n\nEnhance functionality through custom API integrations.\n\nUtilize your knowledge of WordPress, Lightspeed, and Shopify (if applicable) to deliver high-quality digital solutions.\n\nCollaborate with developers, designers, and marketers effectively.\n\nQUALIFICATIONS1-3 years of experience in frontend web development.\n\nWorking knowledge of\n\nWordPress and its plugins like Advanced Custom Fields, Gravity Forms, WPML.\n\nHTML, CSS, Sass, Javascript, jQuery, PHP, and MySQL.\n\nGit and hosting practices.\n\nLightspeed, Shopify\n\nExhibits enthusiasm, a thirst for learning, and sociability.\n\nExcellent communication skills, able to interact with clients and internal teams effectively and professionally,\n\nMust possess a Bachelor's degree, Computer Science / Information Technology, Engineering (Computer / Telecommunication), Mathematics, Science & Technology or equivalent.\n\nJ-18808-Ljbffr\n\nLast updated : 2024-04-10",
